nbc with the us arms of frances thomson sa and the dutch nv 
philips is pushing hard for its extended definition system dubbed 
advanced compatible television 
it would not require the second simulcast system and thus would 
cost broadcasters and consumers much less and could be up and 
running a lot faster 
