the government travel bureau in east berlin all prices for rent 
and groceries will go up but our savings and salaries will go 
down 
we were very optimistic now i dont know if we can live with 
such conditions she said 
the idealism that brought down communism last year has been 
quickly replaced by shock over the cost of capitalism 
some blame west german chancellor helmut kohl for promising them 
western prosperity while campaigning for his political surrogate in 
