reservation in south dakota 
public service in magazine journalism a tie between common 
cause magazine and the new yorker common cause was honored for a 
series of articles on the corrupting influence of money on the 
political process in washington dc the new yorker was cited for 
a series on the possible health hazards of lowlevel 
electromagnetic radiation 
photography patrick davison of the albuquerque nm tribune 
for photographs accompanying a series on the exploitation of elk 
