nutrition education and other aspects of the program will continue 
the program was launched in january 
heartguide was proposed in 1987 as an attempt to uniformly 
identify foods with certain levels of cholesterol fat and sodium 
the foods were to be identified with a heartguide seal of 
approval a heart with a checkmark on the package 
