acid in a murderforprofit scheme in which a productliability 
lawsuit was filed against the maker of quintens baby formula irby 
filed the lawsuit in 1987 against abbott laboratories which 
denied the allegations but withdrew it a year later 
smith 27 was not a party to the lawsuit said her lawyer 
laureen cahill casey 
