christian enclave 
the fighting broke out around midnight shattering a ceasefire 
brokered by vaticanbacked mediators only a few hours earlier 
snow blocked mountain roads and prevented gen michel aouns 
army troops and samir geageas lebanese forces militia from 
launching ground offensives 
at least a dozen fires blazed in the christian enclave in 
