blanket indemnity is not being considered 
but he added with these steps the government proves it is not 
blind to the problems of the moment the groundwork for the 
creation of a climate conducive to negotiation must continue 
the government released seven anc prisoners monday from robben 
island prison off cape town more than 50 activists have been freed 
in the past two months 
