lithuanias president monday invited kremlin 
officials to lithuania to discuss the republics secession drive 
and struck a conciliatory note by saying lithuania wants gradual 
not immediate full independence 
while government officials sought a compromise solution to the 
dispute 1000 proindependence demonstrators rallied at the 
