allegations that iraq tried to smuggle in 40 usmade krytrons or 
electronic detonators for nuclear bomb detonators 
these are only condensors which we bought and its not 
logical that these could be used in atomic bombs he said 
the foreign ministry released photocopies of documents it said 
proved iraqs innocence and showed that a person it identified as 
an fbi agent attempted to lure iraq into ordering the triggers 
it said attempts by british and american authorities to 
portray iraq as a nuclear power are aimed at blackmailing and 
