education program called i have aids a teenagers story a 
321 contact extra which white helped develop it was nominated 
for an emmy and won a george peabody award and an ollie award 
white enjoyed collecting comic books swimming and customizing 
his red mustang he also owned two dogs wally and gizmo although 
