was unable to tell him another thing he wanted was out of reach 
because he had aids 
ryan said its my life and i want a pup he said i want a 
pup that likes no one but me she said 
white was diagnosed as having aids in 1984 when he was 13 he 
contracted the disease through blood products he received to treat 
his hemophilia a disorder that impairs the bloods ability to clot 
and stop bleeding 
i dont think its the aids as much as hes a hemophiliac and 
hes bleeding internally and thats the problem van dyke said 
she said white was in poor health before thanksgiving when they 
prepared several public service announcements for world aids day on 
dec 7 
