here are the names of the 15 men who have 
served as chief justice of the united states with their dates of 
service and the presidents who nominated them 
john jay 17891795 nominated by george washington 
oliver ellsworth 17961800 by washington 
john marshall 18011835 by john adams 
roger b taney 18361864 by andrew jackson 
salmon p chase 18641873 by abraham lincoln 
morrison r waite 18741888 by ulysses grant 
melville w fuller 18881910 by grover cleveland 
edward d white 19101921 by william howard taft 
william howard taft 19211930 by warren harding 
charles evans hughes 19301941 by herbert hoover 
harlan f stone 19411946 by franklin roosevelt 
fred m vinson 19461953 by harry truman 
earl warren 19531969 by dwight eisenhower 
warren e burger 19691986 by richard nixon 
william h rehnquist 1986present by ronald reagan 
