vegetable salad nicoise 
serves 4 
cup zucchini scrubbed ends removed cut lengthwise and then 
in inch slices 
cup yellow summer squash washed ends removed cut in thirds 
lengthwise and then in inch slices 
4 ounces green beans ends removed cut in half 
6 to 8 cherry tomatoes stemmed cut in half 
cup pitted black olives drained and rinsed 
1 6ounce jar of marinated artichoke hearts drained thoroughly 
rinsed and cut in half 
cup vinaigrette dressing 
 
in a pan in two quarts of water over medium heat cook string 
beans until crisp tender six to eight minutes drain and refresh 
under cold water 
in a large bowl combine all the vegetables 
in a small bowl whisk the dressing and pour over salad mix 
throroughly and serve 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
peppers stuffed with stirfried vegetables 
serves 2 
2 red andor green peppers tops removed seeded left whole 
tablespoon sesame oil 
1 tablespoons peanut oil 
1 red pepper seeded cut into inch cubes 
1 green pepper seeded cut into inch cubes 
zucchini cut into inch cubes 
1 yellow delicious apple cored cut into inch cubes 
1 tablespoon sesame seeds toasted in 200degree oven until 
slightly brown 
 
steam the whole peppers for 10 minutes in a steamer 
heat the oil in a skillet or wok add the peppers and zucchini 
cook 3 to 5 minutes stirring occasionally add the apples stir 
fry until the colors are vivid but the texture firm about two 
minutes 
stuff the whole peppers with the stirfried mixture sprinkle 
with sesame seeds and serve 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
quick black bean sauce for baked or broiled fish 
yield 1 cup 
1 tablespoon olive oil 
1 teaspoon sesame oil 
cup finely chopped scallions 
cup finely chopped sweet red pepper 
cup finely chopped celery or summer squash 
2 tablespoons packaged or canned fermented black beans rinsed 
patted dry and finely chopped 
1 canned mild whole green chili rinsed seeded and finely 
chopped 
cup water 
1 tablesoon freshly squeezed lime juice 
1 teaspoon finely chopped peeled fresh gingerroot 
2 to 3 dashes tabasco sauce 
 
in a medium saucepan over medium heat heat the oils add the 
scallions and sweet red pepper and saute until translucent about 
two minutes 
add the beans celery or squash chili lime juice gingerroot 
and tabasco cook about five minutes until the vegetables are 
softened and the sauce is heated through 
remove from heat serve over the fish 
