most pork futures prices rose their permitted daily limits 
monday on the chicago mercantile exchange following a government 
report that indicated 1990 hog production will continue to lag 
behind last years 
on other commodity markets cattle futures advanced soybean 
futures fell sharply while grains were mixed oil futures gained 
and precious metals retreated slightly 
