<TEXT>
dreyers grand ice cream inc said monday it has 
developed a cholesterolfree frozen dessert that it touts as tasing 
like premium ice cream but having only a fraction of the fat and 
onethird fewer calories 
the product called american dream contains less than 1 percent 
fat and 80 calories per threeounce serving the oakland 
califbased food company said 
that compares with 16 percent fat 30 milligrams of cholesterol 
and 120 calories in three ounces of typical premium ice cream the 
company said 
dreyers said it was able to reduce the fat and eliminate 
cholesterol in american dream through a proprietary technology that 
concentrates protein and enables us to use all the same dairy 
ingredients found in ice cream 
that distinguishes it from monsanto cos simple pleasures a 
recently introduced frozen dessert that uses the fat substitute 
simplesse which is made from egg whites and milk protein 
t gary rogers chairman and chief executive of dreyers said 
in a telephone interview that american dream should attract people 
who have been avoiding ice cream because of its fat and cholesterol 
content 
he said it will also enable ice cream eaters to consume more of 
this type of dessert without worrying about cholesterol which is 
believed to contribute to heart and arterial diseases 
in national overthecounter trading dreyers rose 25 cents a 
share to 3275 
rogers said dreyers has used its protein concentration process 
for its light frozen dessert and yogurt products he said that 
although the process is not patented others have been unable to 
duplicate it 
joseph arsenio an analyst who follows dreyers for the 
investment firm hambrecht amp quist in san francisco said his firm 
was enthusiastic about the new product 
it should appeal to an audience that is very cholesterol as 
well as fat conscious he said 
the company plans to sell the dessert in nine flavors and make 
it available in quarts and half gallons rather than the pint sizes 
used for superpremium ice creams it will be priced comparably with 
premium ice cream or about 230 for a quart and 4 for a 
halfgallon the company said 
american dream should reach stores within six to eight weeks 
rogers said 
dreyers said it is the nations thirdlargest ice cream and 
frozen dessert maker with sales of 227 million in 1989 
industrywide sales amounted to 93 billion last year according to 
the international ice cream association trade group 
dreyers makes and distributes its premium ice cream under the 
name dreyers grand in the west and edys grand east of the 
rockies it also makes grand light a frozen dessert with 7 percent 
fat and frozen yogurt inspirations with 3 pecent fat 
rogers said dreyers will spend 24 million marketing all of its 
products this year up from 18 million in 1989 
