the manville property damage settlement trust has 
completed a review of 14000 claims for asbestos exposure and has 
paid 68 million to some of the claimants the trust announced 
monday 
the trust based in white plains ny said in a news statement 
it also has set aside 28 million for settling other claims and 
expects an additional 200 million to be available for distribution 
over the next three years 
the trust was established in 1988 as part of a reorganization of 
denverbsaed manville corp by the us bankruptcy court of the 
southern district of new york 
more than 3000 claimants have submitted claims so far and the 
largest 50 will receive over 25 percent of the money the largest 
200 claimants will receive over 45 percent according to the trust 
of the 13 billion claimed no more than 280 million or 21 
percent can be reimbursed 
the fund was established to resolve millions of dollars in 
damage claims against manville stemming from its days as the 
nations largest asbestos producer 
the company was forced to file for protection from creditors in 
1982 as a result of asbestosrelated lawsuits it emerged from that 
protection in 1988 
among the largest claimants seeking more than 2 million are 
the city of new york united states steel corp the state of 
massachusetts the state of illinois the state of new york and 
the state of texas 
kurt h schaffir the trusts executive director said the trust 
is limited on how much of the final settlement on any claim can be 
paid and how much of this can be distributed at any point in time 
reimbursements are limited to fixed percentages for different 
categories but trust officials say people should still continue to 
file if they think they have a claim 
the rate at which claims are being received has tapered off 
considerably and it is quite possible that sufficient funds will 
be available over the next three years to pay half or more of the 
maximum payable amounts we believe that it continues to be very 
much worthwhile for eligible claimants to file new claims 
schaffir said 
manville founded in 1858 makes building products and packaging 
materials 
